Roy Emerton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roy_Emerton 0 Roy Emerton (9 October 1893 – 30 November 1944) was a British film actor.Earlier in his life, he was a sailor, stoker, docker, railway worker, miner and served in the First World War. He played in a great number of popular London stage plays and shows, including Shakespeare as well as film work.
